# NOTE: Compiled gettext catalogs (locales/*/LC_MESSAGES/*.mo) are
# intentionally NOT ignored — they are committed so that cloning the repo
# does not require the `msgfmt` command to be available. Regenerate them
# with `python tools/msgfmt.py` whenever the .po source changes.
